    "This allows us to observe which topics gained or lost traction over time, offering valuable insights into the shifting dynamics of public perception.",
    "Figure 4 reveals the sentiment distribution for each of the potentially controversial topics selected in our analysis.",
    "The tweets about certain topics such as Education, Marketing, Healthcare, Writing, Prompt Engineering, and Art are more positive whereas the tweets about Cybersecurity, Jobs, and Lawyers are more negative.",
    "In addition, we track the percentage shifts in positive and negative tweets for each topic.",
    "These in-depth trends are shown in Figure 5."
